{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"440","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"宜家家居：2030 年全部產品將以可再生或可回收材料製成","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p style='background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); cursor: text; font-family: sans-serif,Arial,Verdana,&amp;quot;Trebuchet MS&amp;quot;; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20.8px; margin-bottom: 13px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-top: 13px; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;'><img alt='' src='https://tomorrowsci.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/圖片1-678x381.jpg' style='font: 400 13.93px/22.28px open sans,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px rgb(0, 0, 0); border-image: none; width: 800px; height: 450px; text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; text-decoration: none; word-spacing: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; white-space: normal; cursor: default; max-width: 708.94px; orphans: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: 100%; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: transparent;' title='圖片1' /></p>\n\n<p style='background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); cursor: text; font-family: sans-serif,Arial,Verdana,&amp;quot;Trebuchet MS&amp;quot;; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20.8px; margin-bottom: 13px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-top: 13px; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='background-color: transparent; border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: open sans,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: 100%; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6px; margin-bottom: 24px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-top: 0px; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;'><strong style='border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; font-family: open sans,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: 100%; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 700; line-height: 25.6px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;'>全球最大家具零售商宜家家居（IKEA）在最新發表的永續發展報告中表示，2018 </strong><strong style='border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; font-family: open sans,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: 100%; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 700; line-height: 25.6px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;'>年其產品中有 70%</strong><strong style='border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; font-family: open sans,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: 100%; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 700; line-height: 25.6px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;'>&nbsp;</strong><strong style='border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; font-family: open sans,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: 100%; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 700; line-height: 25.6px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;'>的材料是可再生或可回收的，希望能在 2030 </strong><strong style='border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; font-family: open sans,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: 100%; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 700; line-height: 25.6px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;'>年達到全部產品使用可再生或可回收材料製成</strong><strong style='border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; font-family: open sans,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: 100%; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 700; line-height: 25.6px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;'>的目標。</strong></p>\n\n<h2 style='background-color: transparent; border-bottom-color: rgb(20, 144, 206); border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: rgb(20, 144, 206); border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: rgb(20, 144, 206); border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: rgb(20, 144, 206); border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; color: rgb(20, 144, 206); font-family: headline-semi-bold,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 24px; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: 100%; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 31.2px; margin-bottom: 24px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-top: 0px; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;'>永續發展報告</h2>\n\n<p style='background-color: transparent; border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: open sans,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: 100%; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6px; margin-bottom: 24px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-top: 0px; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;'>長達 59 頁的永續發展報告顯示，宜家在 2018 年採購的所有原料中有 60% 屬於可再生材料，如棉花和竹子，還有 10% 來自消費前（pre-consumer）或消費後（post-consumer）的可回收材料。該報告聲稱宜家有望於 2030 年達到 100% ，但需要與工業界合作，為木材、塑料和布料等回收材料建立更大的供應鏈。此外，宜家製造供應鏈中 86.7% 的供暖和 81.1% 的電力需求由再生能源供應。</p>\n\n<p style='background-color: transparent; border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: open sans,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: 100%; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6px; margin-bottom: 24px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-top: 0px; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;'>宜家母公司英特宜家集團（Inter Ikea Group）的永續發展負責人莉娜&middot;普里普-科瓦奇（Lena Pripp-Kovac）在報告中表示：「我們始終抱持遠見與創新，以確保今天滿足我們這一代需求的行為，不會犧牲後代滿足需求的能力。這需要我們重新思考和激發生活方式及消費的變化，並改變我們的工作方式──從線性到循環，從消費到再生資源。」</p>\n\n<h2 style='background-color: transparent; border-bottom-color: rgb(20, 144, 206); border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: rgb(20, 144, 206); border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: rgb(20, 144, 206); border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: rgb(20, 144, 206); border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; color: rgb(20, 144, 206); font-family: headline-semi-bold,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 24px; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: 100%; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 31.2px; margin-bottom: 24px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-top: 0px; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;'>減少氣候足跡</h2>\n\n<p style='background-color: transparent; border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: open sans,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: 100%; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6px; margin-bottom: 24px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-top: 0px; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;'>宜家希望將氣候科學融入公司價值鏈考量，從而減少排放並為達成巴黎協議做出貢獻。具體目標是在 2030 年將店面與營運產生的氣候足跡（climate footprint）減少至 2016 年的 80% 。宜家聲稱若能在 2030 年從價值鏈減少 15% 的排放量，將意味著每個產品平均減少 70% 的氣候足跡。因此，宜家正致力於從關鍵材料、食品成分和運輸等部分著手脫碳（decarbonise），同時為直接供應商制定更加積極的減排目標。</p>\n\n<p style='background-color: transparent; border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: open sans,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: 100%; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6px; margin-bottom: 24px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-top: 0px; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;'>根據永續發展報告，宜家 2018 年價值鏈的氣候足跡比 2016 年高 2.8%，主要是由於業務的擴張。整體氣候足跡的主要貢獻來自原材料（36.4%）、家用產品（22.2%）以及顧客到店與宅配的運輸（15.5%）。報告同時解釋：「將我們的增長與溫室氣體排放分離需要時間，我們預計排放量會在減少之前再增加幾年。」</p>\n\n<h2 style='background-color: transparent; border-bottom-color: rgb(20, 144, 206); border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: rgb(20, 144, 206); border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: rgb(20, 144, 206); border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: rgb(20, 144, 206); border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; color: rgb(20, 144, 206); font-family: headline-semi-bold,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 24px; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: 100%; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 31.2px; margin-bottom: 24px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-top: 0px; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;'>恰如其分的生活</h2>\n\n<p style='background-color: transparent; border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: open sans,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: 100%; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6px; margin-bottom: 24px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-top: 0px; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;'>該報告還列出了宜家實現永續發展目標之前的其他挑戰，包括改善整個供應鏈的工作條件、擴充價值鏈報告的必要性，以及在群眾間激發新的永續消費模式的急迫性。</p>\n\n<p style='background-color: transparent; border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: open sans,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: 100%; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6px; margin-bottom: 24px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-top: 0px; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;'>宜家的「Live Lagom」活動長期以來一直在解決後者的這項挑戰，Lagom 是瑞典文化「不多不少」的哲學，引導消費者不浪費資源或能源，創造和諧生活的家園。該計劃將推出數十種創新產品，旨在使家居生活更具可持續性，包括素肉丸、使用 100% 消費後回收（post-consumer recycled, PCR）材料和節能照明的廚房。</p>\n\n<p style='background-color: transparent; border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom-style: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-image-outset: 0; border-image-repeat: stretch; border-image-slice: 100%; border-image-source: none; border-image-width: 1; border-left-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-left-style: none; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-right-style: none; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-top-style: none; border-top-width: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: open sans,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: 100%; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 25.6px; margin-bottom: 24px; marg